<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The QWaylandIdleInhibitV1 extension provides a way for a client to inhibit the idle behavior of the compositor when a specific surface is visually relevant to the user.</db:para>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qwaylandidleinhibitmanagerv1.xml">QWaylandIdleInhibitManagerV1</db:link> corresponds to the Wayland interface, <db:code>zwp_idle_inhibit_manager_v1</db:code>.</db:para>
<db:para>Inhibited surfaces have the QWaylandSurface::inhibitsIdle property set to <db:code>true</db:code>.</db:para>
